e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T12:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將電話socket去房B socket果條cat 5 甩走佢(如果房唔用電話嘅話，唔係佢會lock死你房a去房b條cat5)<br />\n之後房A去房B條cat5跟番socket啲色打，照道理房a modem吉落socket入，再係房b socket出就用到</blockquote><br />\nlock死係點？"},{"pid":"e9f9b051768ad2550d14f1577f21faf3bd29766f","tid":375240,"uid":81340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:04:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ihdqnrwf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fihdqnrwf&h=b4e6a01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果電話插咗落廳個座度，會唔會影響我嘅方法？</blockquote><br />\n屌 A同B調轉咗</blockquote><br />\n你邊張圖先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tn0g81x6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftn0g81x6&h=c9644d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根據我物理學既電路知識好似有啲虧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就噤望 room b 座 , 接左1, 2 條cat5係for 上網, 接左3,4 果條係電話( 如果裝修係跟線色)<br />\n但條上網cat5 係唔係去room a 我就好有保留, 因為本身設計我唔會覺得專登放條cat5 由room a 去 room b for 上網, 你room a 條cat5 應該係電話用去左廳或其他地方, 但一切都係跟你幅圖估, 唔能作準<br />\n你要確定接左room b 橙色果組去左邊先可以做下一步"},{"pid":"0c4678699e21b521728025748fb0fae8b34712d6","tid":375240,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/p08imzda\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp08imzda&h=978a490e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想用房A去房B條暗喉嘅cat5e線令到房B可以用lan線上網，方法大概係router插入去房B個座。"},{"pid":"78c77b937841511dd7385cc3a5c3f25a6c80a5dc","tid":375240,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/p08imzda\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fp08imzda&h=978a490e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我想用房A去房B條暗喉嘅cat5e線令到房B可以用lan線上網，方法大概係router插入去房<span style=\"color: blue;\">A</span>個座。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0c334ff025d0468d997712349a62d0284dcb143f","tid":375240,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ihdqnrwf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fihdqnrwf&h=b4e6a01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果電話插咗落廳個座度，會唔會影響我嘅方法？</blockquote><br />\n屌 A同B調轉咗</blockquote><br />\n你邊張圖先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tn0g81x6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftn0g81x6&h=c9644d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根據我物理學既電路知識好似有啲虧？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就噤望 room b 座 , 接左1, 2 條cat5係for 上網, 接左3,4 果條係電話( 如果裝修係跟線色)<br />\n但條上網cat5 係唔係去room a 我就好有保留, 因為本身設計我唔會覺得專登放條cat5 由room a 去 room b for 上網, 你room a 條cat5 應該係電話用去左廳或其他地方, 但一切都係跟你幅圖估, 唔能作準<br />\n你要確定接左room b 橙色果組去左邊先可以做下一步</blockquote><br />\n睇下面嘅新圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7038a17dec7995cd74f4db1eff468b85a7be182","tid":375240,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ihdqnrwf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fihdqnrwf&h=b4e6a01b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果電話插咗落廳個座度，會唔會影響我嘅方法？</blockquote><br />\n屌